chan = Rails.configuration.slack_channels.horizons_polaris

header "❄️ welcome to polaris!"

section <<~TEXT, markdown: true
  You've just been added to <##{chan}>, the channel for Horizons Polaris in Toronto! For more info, check out [horizons.hackclub.com/polaris](https://horizons.hackclub.com/polaris).

  Head over and introduce yourself!
TEXT
